ight.exe is installed in 'C:\\Users\\LWS\\AppData\\Roaming\\Python\\Python314\\Scripts' which is not on PATH.\r\n  Consider adding this directory to PATH or, if you prefer to suppress this warning, use --no-warn-script-location.\r\n\r\nSuccessfully installed greenlet-3.3.2 playwright-1.58.0 pyee-13.0.1\r\n\r\n[notice] A new release of pip is available: 25.3 -> 26.0.1\r\n[notice] To update, run: python.exe -m pip install --upgrade pip\r\n","name":"pip install"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774572954026}}
{"type":"message","id":"d9d1030a","parentId":"ee6b14c0","timestamp":"2026-03-27T00:56:01.767Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Playwright 安装成功了！现在需要安装浏览器驱动。Playwright 需要安装 Chromium 浏览器才能运行。\n\n但是，要实现\"自动获取主人已登录浏览器的 Cookie\"，有几种方案：\n\n1. **使用浏览器的用户数据目录**：用 Playwright 打开主人的 Chrome/Edge 浏览器（带用户数据目录），这样可以直接复用已登录的 Cookie。但这需要知道主人浏览器的用户数据目录路径。\n\n2. **扫码登录方案**：用 Playwright 打开一个新浏览器，让主人扫码登录咸鱼，然后自动提取 Cookie。\n\n3. **更简单的方式**：其实主人已经在浏览器登录了咸鱼，最简单的方式是让我写一个 Python 脚本，用 Playwright 连接到已运行的浏览器（通过 DevTools Protocol），然后提取 Cookie。\n\n但最实用、最简单的方案其实是：既然 Playwright 已经安装了，我可以创建一个脚本，打开浏览器让主人扫码登录，然后自动提取 Cookie 并保存。\n\n不过，考虑到复杂度和时间，我觉得应该跟主人说明：\n1. 自动获取已登录浏览器的 Cookie 技术上比较复杂（需要连接已运行的浏览器）\n2. 更简单的方式是：我用 Playwright 打开一个新浏览器窗口，主人扫码登录，然后我自动提取 Cookie\n\n让我先安装 Playwright 的浏览器，然后创建自动化脚本。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Playwright 安装完成啦~ 现在需要安装浏览器驱动！\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_88f78b5ebbcf4912ac442b19","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd $env:USERPROFILE\\.xianyu-agent; playwright install chromium","yieldMs":60000}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-llm-chudian-site","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":34849,"output":626,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":35475,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774572954031,"responseId":"chatcmpl-d6888298-afcd-9bfb-89bd-f358adb80ff7"}}
