{"type":"message","id":"dc287b94","parentId":"1e5c0ccc","timestamp":"2026-03-27T00:57:10.572Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"太好了，Playwright 浏览器安装完成！现在我需要创建一个 Python 脚本来自动获取 Cookie。\n\n但是有个问题：主人说\"我的咸鱼已在网页登录，请你自己去获取 cookie\"，这意味着主人已经在某个浏览器（Chrome/Edge）中登录了咸鱼。要获取这个已登录浏览器的 Cookie，有几种方案：\n\n1. **连接已运行的浏览器**：使用 Chrome DevTools Protocol (CDP) 连接到主人已打开的浏览器。但这需要主人先在浏览器中启用远程调试端口（启动时加 --remote-debugging-port=9222 参数），比较复杂。\n\n2. **复制浏览器用户数据目录**：找到主人浏览器的用户数据目录（包含 Cookie 文件），然后用 Playwright 带着这个目录启动浏览器。但 Cookie 文件通常被浏览器锁定，且可能加密。\n\n3. **最简单实用的方案**：用 Playwright 打开一个新浏览器窗口，显示二维码让主人扫码登录，登录成功后自动提取 Cookie 并保存。\n\n我觉得方案 3 最实际。让我创建一个 Python 脚本来实现这个功能。\n\n不过，等一下——其实还有一个更简单的方案：\n\n**方案 4**：既然主人已经在浏览器登录了，我可以用 Playwright 的 `connect_over_cdp` 功能，但需要主人先关闭浏览器，然后用特殊参数重新启动。\n\n或者，我可以让主人直接手动复制 Cookie（这是最快速的），同时我开发一个自动化脚本供将来使用。\n\n\n我现在要写一个 Python 脚本来实现扫码登录和 Cookie 自动提取的功能。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"浏览器安装完成啦~ 现在我来创建一个自动化脚本，可以打开浏览器让主人扫码登录，然后自动提取 Cookie！\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_b8ee999228904dc9b01e7050","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"~/.xianyu-agent/get_cookie_auto.py","content":"#!/usr/bin/env python\n# -*- coding: utf-8 -*-\n\"\"\"\n闲鱼 Cookie 自动获取脚本\n使用 Playwright 打开浏览器，用户扫码登录后自动提取 Cookie\n\"\"\"\n\nimport json\nimport os\nimport sys\nfrom pathlib import Path\nfrom playwright.sync_api import sync_playwright\n\ndef get_cookie():\n    \"\"\"打开浏览器，让用户扫码登录，然后提取 Cookie\"\"\"\n    \n    xianyu_dir = Path.home() / \".xianyu-agent\"\n    xianyu_dir.mkdir(exist_ok=True)\n    \n    print(\"🐟 闲鱼 Cookie 自动获取工具\")\n    print(\"=\" * 50)\n    print()\n    print(\"即将打开浏览器，请访问闲鱼网页版并扫码登录...\")\n    print()\n    print(\"登录步骤：\")\n    print(\"1. 浏览器会自动打开闲鱼网站\")\n    print(\"2. 使用支付宝/淘宝 APP 扫码登录\")\n    print(\"3. 登录成功后，Cookie 会自动提取并保存\")\n    print()\n    input(\"按回车键继续...\")\n    \n    with sync_playwright() as p:\n        # 启动浏览器（可见模式）\n        browser = p.chromium.launch(headless=False, args=[\n            '--window-size=1280,800',\n        ])\n        \n        # 创建新上下文\n        context = browser.new_context(\n            viewport={'width': 1280, 'height': 800},\n            user_agent='Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/120.0.0.0 Safari/537.36'\n        )\n        \n        page = context.new_page()\n        \n        # 导航到闲鱼\n        print(\"正在打开闲鱼网站...\")\n        page.goto('https://www.goofish.com/', wait_until='networkidle')\n        \n        print(\"请在打开的浏览器窗口中扫码登录...\")\n        print(\"等待登录完成（最长 120 秒）...\")\n        \n        # 等待登录（检测 Cookie 中的关键字段）\n        max_wait = 120  # 最多等 120 秒\n        check_interval = 2  # 每 2 秒检查一次\n        elapsed = 0\n        \n        while elapsed < max_wait:\n            cookies = context.cookies()\n            cookie_dict = {c['name']: c['value'] for c in cookies}\n            \n            # 检查是否有登录必需的 Cookie\n            if 'unb' in cookie_dict and '_m_h5_tk' in cookie_dict:\n                print()\n                print(\"✅ 检测到登录成功！\")\n                break\n            \n            elapsed += check_interval\n            page.wait_for_timeout(check_interval * 1000)\n            \n            # 显示进度\n            if elapsed % 10 == 0:\n                print(f\"  已等待 {elapsed} 秒...\")\n        \n        # 获取所有 Cookie\n        cookies = context.cookies()\n        cookie_dict = {c['name']: c['value'] for c in cookies}\n        \n        # 检查是否成功获取必要字段\n        if 'unb' not in cookie_dict or '_m_h5_tk' not in cookie_dict:\n            print()\n            print(\"❌ 超时未检测到登录，请重试\")\n            browser.close()\n            return None\n        \n        # 构建 Cookie 字符串\n        cookie_string = \"; \".join([f\"{c['name']}={c['value']}\" for c in cookies])\n        \n        print()\n        print(\"✅ Cookie 提取成功！\")\n        print()\n        \n        # 保存到配置文件\n        config = {\n            \"cookie\": cookie_string,\n            \"created_at\": str(Path.home() / \".xianyu-agent\"),\n            \"auto_reply\": True,\n            \"simulate_typing\": False,\n            \"heartbeat_interval\": 15,\n            \"message_expire_time\": 300000\n        }\n        \n        config_path = xianyu_dir / \"config.json\"\n        with open(config_path, 'w', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n            json.dump(config, f, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2)\n        \n        print(f\"📁 配置文件已保存：{config_path}\")\n        print()\n        \n        # 验证关键字段\n        print(\"Cookie 验证：\")\n        print(f\"  - 用户 ID (unb): {cookie_dict.get('unb', '❌ 缺失')[:10]}...\")\n        print(f\"  - Token (_m_h5_tk): {cookie_dict.get('_m_h5_tk', '❌ 缺失')[:20]}...\")\n        print()\n        \n        browser.close()\n        \n        return cookie_string\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    try:\n        cookie = get_cookie()\n        if cookie:\n            print(\"🎉 Cookie 获取完成！可以启动自动回复服务了~\")\n            sys.exit(0)\n        else:\n            print(\"❌ Cookie 获取失败\")\n            sys.exit(1)\n    except Exception as e:\n        print(f\"❌ 错误：{e}\")\n        sys.exit(1)\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-llm-chudian-site","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":37326,"output":1893,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":39219,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774573006385,"responseId":"chatcmpl-00690a94-fa68-9890-b0d5-01fce9aa0153"}}
